reviews.customers_say: Customers love this sweater's oversized fit that pairs well with leggings, and appreciate its gorgeous color.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love it!
items.body: I absolutely love this sweater! I am at an age where I no longer like sweaters much because one minute I'm hot and the next cold. That said, I needed something warm and nice to wear for an outdoor ceremony and this was perfect. It's super soft and cozy and perfect with thermals, a T-shirt or a turtleneck underneath. Or, just the sweater works too , but I like to be able to strip during those hot flashes haha! I love that it can be worn casual with jeans or leggings, or dressed up with a long midi skirt. Either way, it's well made and it will be well loved by me! For reference I'm 5'3" and about 175lbs. I bought the XL and I LOVE it! It's oversized but not so baggy that it looks sloppy and that's how I like it. I thought it would be super heavy; I would say mid weight and probably why I like it so much. The black and white is great with some checkered leggings that I have but works perfectly with plain black ones, too. This sweater is well made and well worth what I paid for it. I would purchase again! Read more
items.author: pixybrat

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars High quality
items.body: High quality with high end look, soft, thick material, perfect over size sweater. Read more
items.author: Lainey

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sizing May Vary Shirt to Shirt
items.body: This is a rewrite of a review I wrote after receiving the second color of the same sweater that I ordered in 2 colors at the same time. The pictures I've shared here are of the SECOND one I received. I didn't take pictures of the first one before I returned it. This sweater is very soft and well made. Very true to color in the listing. When I got the first one in gray, I really wanted to love it because of the color and the fabric but it was just too large. For reference I am 5'6" 140lbs. I ordered a large in both colors at the same time because I really like the oversized fit, but this was already quite oversized. I received the second color (apricot) several days later and it was a much different story. Still oversized like I wanted but not overwhelming like the first one. I would describe the fit as sort of a loose bubble. Sleeves very long and on the first one I got were very loose at the ends. The second one had sleeve ends that were more snug and didn't fall off my hands. Even if I kept the first one, the sleeves would have been a problem falling down off the ends of my hands. I want to comment on the color since screens and lighting can make a difference - this apricot named color I'm wearing in the picture I would describe as oatmeal. Maybe toasted oatmeal. It's a very neutral color easy to wear with other colors. I really LOVE this sweater and may try to re-order other colors and take my chances I'll end up with one that fits the way I like. Read more
items.author: Becky

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very nice & attractive.
items.body: Very nice sweater. Appreciate when the item is as advertised. Soft substantial material, but not overly heavy. Color is as pictured and the contrasting color accent is flattering. Loose fit but not oversized. This casual piece looks good with pants or a skirt. Thumbs up! Read more
items.author: CF

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars OBSESSED! Feels Like a Blanket and Works for Everything
items.body: The softness is amazing—it's buttery soft and truly feels like I'm wearing a blanket all day long. That feeling contributes to an absolutely amazing comfort level! The quality of the sweater is fantastic; the material is a good thick weight that keeps me nice and warm without feeling heavy. I'm already planning to go back and buy more in different colors! The size is perfect because it's so versatile. It's the ideal oversized look to wear with leggings, but you can also easily tuck it in with jeans or even wear it with work pants—I wore it to my freezing-cold office, and it was perfect. Read more
items.author: Kiley Straub

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars YOU NEED THIS!
items.body: LOVE THIS! it is so cute and comfortable its oversized perfect for winter or even fall. You can style it with leggings or jeans and its cute! Read more
items.author: Britts

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Adorable and Stylish
items.body: I want this in every color and style they have! As someone who is right between an XXL and 1X, I've tried the L and XL from this brand and they both fit well. The size difference is basically a more neat, clean fit that goes well with jeans or a looser, comfy fit with leggings. Both ways look stylish. I've worn this a few times and there are some very minor snags that would happen to any sweater. They are definitely thick and versatile, so a couple of little snags will not bother me because overall they seem very durable. Read more
items.author: C

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Very nice sweater but 1st impressions are lasting
items.body: Very nice sweater but the packaging wasn’t great (looked tried on previously) and sweater arrived with a large hole in one of the sleeves. I would have kept it but this was laziness on the shippers end. Read more
items.author: K. Wright

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Stripe Green, Double Gray, Stripe Orange, Color Black, Color Camel, Stripe Apricot, Double Khaki, Double Apricot, Pure Black, Pure Apricot, Pure Coffee, Stripe Navy, Pure Green, Pure Gray. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
